Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins. I work with troubled teenagers that are involved with drugs, and I guess I'm looking for some wisdom as to how to encourage them to raise their consciousness, to, you know, to look beyond that and find something, especially if they're depressed, one of them just lost his best friend, use that as an excuse to go get on drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your life and for your teachings, I appreciate them so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with the relationship of the teaching...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings and the whole process of enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and how that relates to developing an organization, a clinic, a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How that relates to a hospital or a clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't relate to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering, other than having staff who have maximum consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is there anything in particular, obstacles that I can be aware of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,to help improve the ability of a clinic to bring healing to persons?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the clinical reflects who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.44,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and the clinic I had back east reflected, in all of its functions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I had become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was spiritually oriented, so I encouraged the Course in Miracles people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to establish an attitudinal healing center.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All the AAs in Long Island used to come there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.43,0:07:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and we gave free B12 shots once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we encourage people to do the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a hopeless disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you take the Course in Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you recover, it's terrific, and if you don't, you won't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do the Course, you're not going to give a damn one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you uplift people by that which you have become.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you get the leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader is going to radiate out the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we favored everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Free, alternative, anything that would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing on your head and eating oatmeal upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If that helped, we'd try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And we tried all kinds of things that other people would consider wacky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rotation diets, cerebral allergy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I had patients that would get, you know, we'd take 1 to 10,000 dilution of potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember putting it under his tongue, and he became psychotic right on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.50,0:08:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we gave him a neutralizing dose, and the psychosis disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all things that traditional medicine pooh-poohed, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told the story many a time about the lady who was getting the 5-hour glucose tolerance test,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and we would do serial electroencephalograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And during the fifth hour after her blood sugar shot down like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,she tore all her clothes off and ran down Northern Boulevard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stark naked, running down the sidewalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And the lab director, as I say, he was like Ichabod Crane, about 6'6", in a big skinny pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In his white coat, flying behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Mr. Crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Ms. Dawson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back, Ms. Dawson.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the cars jammed each other under her butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the traditional medical person was pooh-poohing hypoglycemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman became psychotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.80,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran down the street stark naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're going to pooh-poo it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to pooh-poo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And the blood sugar goes from, you know, 160 and rockets down to 60 in a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can become very psychotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the dedication to do everything you can to be of help to the patient and their family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that's spiritual, consciousness, psychological, physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that's physical, mental, and spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're doing what you can do for a patient, you've got to be operating on all three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, the energy field of the doctor has a bigger impact than the modality used.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he fired scotches by the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them had terrific responses on almost everybody, and others just constantly didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:10:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you hold in mind who you are, holds in mind that this person's going to get better and improve and fulfill their potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the doctor's attitude has a bigger, you know, because of the Heisenberg principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the Heisenberg principle hasn't been studied from the viewpoint of the consciousness level of the observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's take the average scientist, you know, at 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an integrist as far as he understands truth, but he's not a walking miracle worker at 400 either, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can have somebody who holds in mind great love for all of his patients, and he treats them because he loves them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And his patients recover all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they don't, they don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to train them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can remember things again, it's going to be swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't, what the hell's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say to the wife, don't let them drive anymore, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept practicing because a couple of my old-time patients were so dependent on me, I couldn't dare to wait until they died, and then I quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy used to smoke with the oxygen tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to wait until he left the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the love, you know, you have a love for your patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You hold them in that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a possessive, controlling love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding them in the light of divine love, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget, everybody is fulfilling their own karmic destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that a patient doesn't get better is not exactly a catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You pray for somebody to get sober.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They roll over a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as they roll over the car, they get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the car crashes and they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from your viewpoint, you think it was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In this door, you get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, unless you use kinesiology to diagnose how the case went,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't know whether it was a success or a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes intervention prevents a person from learning the karmic lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that the whole thing was set up to provide for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to thank you so much for your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a gift to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And we all appreciate them very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel compelled to ask you where my vibration is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel compelled to ask you what my calibration is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.75,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You look on the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what your predominant attitude is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How you see God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How you see your fellow man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your prevailing emotionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can pretty much guess it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're angry all the time, that's where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so you're not there, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be here if you were below 200 anyway, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing you've got to, you know, worry is not the right word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing to be concerned about is whether you're above 200 or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,When they're on, the rest is obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're over 200, the rest is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting over the 200, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the lure and the seduction of power over people and the fun of cruelty and winning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,at any cost and killing your enemy, I mean, you know, the payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you can get off the payoff of below 200, the rest you don't have to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're over 200, you don't have to worry unless you fall for some major trap, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to bed with your followers and some craziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're friendly, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.48,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, are we supposed to protect ourselves or is there a way to protect ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,from falling to a lower level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual integrity is the only thing you can follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, of course, spiritual education.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't born with a spiritual education.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:14:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:14:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We are that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to good karma, we pull to ourselves teachings and teachers that provide us with the information
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.94,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that we need, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We follow, you know, our belief systems to the best we can, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you pray for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget you're praying for divine help all along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is concerning prayer, and I know there's been some things talked about, about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,prayer today already, and like if it raises the calibration of your food and stuff, I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,know it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,works but if we can't pray for karma to interfere with karma some somebody else or ourselves or
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:16:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,praying for selfish things like a new car or whatever can you give me some feedback on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the importance why we pray and what for and whatever pray for it you can pray about it but
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,not for it so what's the general no you just surrendered to god's will yeah i have an issue
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with that i have a hard time with that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sorry that's true of everything currently well you'd see you you work on surrendering god's will
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.66,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it's running to god's will about such matters and you hold in mind you hold in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you value and desire what you desire and value what you hold in mind tends to manifest
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when you've
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,got karmic permission see having cheated a lot of people for a lot of lifetimes you may have to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:17:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,wait a while before you get wealthy in this lifetime that's it yeah okay i've noticed some
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of those things that you said the things you hold in mind or your esteem will come what you hold in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,mind tends to manifest i've noticed that already and then you pray and then you pray for and you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender your will to god you know and you say you know if it's your will for me then
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to be able to do that you're not going to be able to do that you're not going to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to do that so you pray about it yeah you pray about it you know you picture what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's karmically permitted it manifests sometimes years later you can picture the ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,situation and then it doesn't manifest for some time you know right but in the meantime you just
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.21,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,hold it in mind okay um also i brought along a dollar first one today i see oh it's got forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,words on it can we okay let me and who we trust
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,oh mail this to michael
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it says those horrible words cross them out crossing it out and mailing it to michael
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,i shouldn't make beat up on michael do i get the hug though he wants a hug you have to be very
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,gentle yeah yeah okay okay yeah thanks we shouldn't beat up on michael oh wait
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.24,0:18:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Thank you for your teachings. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, there's something I'm trying to clear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'm trying to clear up, a life situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:19:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,About two years ago, I sold my business, and I figured I wanted to dedicate my life to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.10,0:19:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to dedicate myself to enlightenment, to truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I figured I will find work that will help me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been two years, and I'm still not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know, is it calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's supposed to happen on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this supposed to be that I'm not supposed to be working?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, you're making it too linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not what you do, it's how you are within the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What you become within the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what you've become, it's irrelevant what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.85,0:19:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you work in a factory, whether you're a shoemaker, whether you're a clerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no difference what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed the lack of graciousness in society is such that when you are really appreciative of somebody,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,they about fall over, they about fall over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, nobody's nice to this clerk all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you say, you know, I think this is the greatest store.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a store in town that I just love, and I think the people there are just stunning, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say, wow, where did all these people come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do, they say, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a hardware store.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hardware store?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no matter what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to get a scissors, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, I'll get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees me as an elderly gentleman, you know, he's in his early twenties.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And he goes over and picks up the scissors, or whatever you call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what I did, somebody was there to like quickly help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's like an energy in the place that they all are aligned with that energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like, for me not to work is a positionality that I'm holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That I feel that it would hold me back in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it won't hold you back because you can be benevolent wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's best just to find a job and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be in the boardroom of a giant corporation, and your benevolence and your integrity influences others, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the obstacle to their non-integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They've got to get past your vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So work to not to work is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how you are within the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that store that I'm speaking of, they think I'm a funny character too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, my wife went in there later to get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And they told him about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Some gentleman was in here and just bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wasn't supposed to be driving all by himself in town either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So how does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Work will come to me that I'm supposed to be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or just something I have to go out and just grab?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Why don't you get a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I live in Washington, D.C. I mean, I live in Seattle, Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Seattle. Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. So anything appeal to you? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I used to do computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go back to doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.59,0:22:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's the energy with which you do a thing and the way you are with it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What you are to the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're saying is I don't want to just punch a keyboard all day, and I can understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What you want is something with grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something with greater human interaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would prefer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.84,0:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so then there's all kinds of humanitarian societies that I'm sure would be happy to start you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I'd start.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the Salvation Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I always envy them at Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.17,0:22:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to stand there with a kettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.17,0:22:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you like to be a Salvation Army person?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you bless all the people and send them love, and they put money in the pot, and you take the money pot home,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.17,0:22:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and that helps poor people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.25,0:23:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So I suggest you sign up for the Salvation Army for the holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.25,0:23:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, very good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.25,0:23:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you give back what you give out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if you volunteer to help, say, in a homeless shelter, you give that back in some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, since you have been working for two years, it might be good to volunteer some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, very good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to sell poppies for the VFW.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to collect money for the Salvation Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to collect money for the Boy Scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to collect my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.61,0:23:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.83,0:23:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just, it's going to take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.19,0:23:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering everything to God, and then asking to see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I think the Course in Miracles works, because the Holy Spirit recontextualizes it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and now when it's recontextualized, you see there's nothing to forgive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.50,0:24:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's just being what they want to be, what they think they need to be, what they feel called to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's times where I just feel like crying, and so I do, and then I feel like, ah, ego got me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.27,0:24:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's okay, because crying is an emotion, but you don't want emotions to run you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.53,0:24:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.01,0:24:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.58,0:24:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.58,0:24:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.46,0:24:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.18,0:24:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this mic positioned correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.18,0:24:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my cheek.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.29,0:24:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.29,0:24:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.29,0:24:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.29,0:24:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.29,0:24:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been told that in order to bring about manifestation, you have to have a lot of strong emotions to desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.29,0:24:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And according to your...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.29,0:24:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Desire holds it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.29,0:24:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Desire is negating that it belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.29,0:24:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:25:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Desire is a negation, because when you become all that you can be, all that you could possibly seek is given to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.90,0:25:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of the fact that you hold it in mind, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.85,0:25:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So holding something in mind with strong emotions doesn't tend to...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.46,0:25:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the strong emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the strong emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.46,0:25:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the emotions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.46,0:25:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.66,0:25:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.66,0:25:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.66,0:25:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.74,0:25:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.74,0:25:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Drivenness is another issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.74,0:25:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Drivenness is another issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.74,0:25:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are moments when drivenness is the way you break through a barrier, so that isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.75,0:25:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole answer that I give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.11,0:25:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger Bannister effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.11,0:26:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it gritting your teeth and deciding you will not accept the limitation and you drive
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.93,0:26:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,through it with...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.98,0:26:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.26,0:26:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.43,0:26:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When I contemplate the field or the context, it becomes difficult to think sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.43,0:26:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,which is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.43,0:26:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.29,0:26:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.29,0:26:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I love being in that mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.29,0:26:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The work I do for a living...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.29,0:26:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.29,0:26:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...is intensely mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.29,0:26:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.29,0:26:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.29,0:26:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.29,0:26:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.29,0:26:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do for a living is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.29,0:26:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Intensely mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.29,0:26:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Intensely mental.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.29,0:26:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.29,0:26:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.29,0:26:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.29,0:26:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.29,0:26:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.29,0:26:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if it's possible to stay in that contemplative mode where I'm more
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.29,0:26:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,attentive to the context and do mental work, or is it time for me to look for different...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.29,0:26:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you become quite advanced at it, yes, you can do it all by yourself because you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.29,0:26:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,don't identify with the linear processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.51,0:27:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you no longer identify with the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.51,0:27:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So mentalization, left brain linear processing, you don't identify with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.74,0:27:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.74,0:27:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You just witness that it's a phenomenon going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.74,0:27:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.74,0:27:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But at a certain point of spiritual evolution, you may not be able to do left brain linear
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.50,0:27:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.50,0:27:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.50,0:27:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.50,0:27:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.50,0:27:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.50,0:27:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.50,0:27:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult for you sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.50,0:27:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.50,0:27:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.50,0:27:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.50,0:27:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes with an instruction book, I'm not going to take it out of the package.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.50,0:27:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.79,0:27:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you can live in this aura and be functional is such a gift to the rest of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.79,0:27:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.79,0:27:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.79,0:27:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't always do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.79,0:27:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't always do it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.79,0:27:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She blisses out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.79,0:27:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.79,0:27:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.11,0:27:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.73,0:27:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.98,0:28:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, last month, you told us that the group as a whole, Nan Callaghan, is a
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.14,0:28:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.14,0:28:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nan calibrates at 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.14,0:28:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The group...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.57,0:28:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.57,0:28:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The group calibrates...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.57,0:28:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.83,0:28:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The group...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.83,0:28:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This group started out at about 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.83,0:28:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.83,0:28:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's now just over 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.83,0:28:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you say about what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.83,0:28:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.83,0:28:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.83,0:28:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because generally, people first are readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.83,0:28:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So they'll read something like Power Versus Force, and they'll say, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.83,0:28:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, you know, then they'll find the author wrote something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.83,0:28:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they discover the...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.83,0:28:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.28,0:28:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.28,0:28:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.28,0:28:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.28,0:28:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.28,0:28:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.28,0:28:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.28,0:28:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.28,0:28:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.42,0:28:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.42,0:28:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.42,0:28:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.42,0:28:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.42,0:28:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.42,0:28:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And they slice the...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.42,0:28:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They practically give them the power...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.42,0:28:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.42,0:28:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a reporter's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.42,0:28:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.42,0:28:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,About...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.42,0:28:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,About 200 million Baht's of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.42,0:28:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bulany, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.82,0:28:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.82,0:28:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.82,0:28:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And in, you know, approximately 300 million dollars worth of resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.82,0:28:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So now...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.05,0:28:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.05,0:28:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred and...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.05,0:28:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.05,0:28:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.05,0:28:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.05,0:28:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to another boy who's at...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.05,0:28:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.05,0:28:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.05,0:29:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.05,0:29:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,People call him Bill Lpatte.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.05,0:29:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bill Lpatte's uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.05,0:29:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.05,0:29:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.04,0:29:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.04,0:29:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He leads everything from Disney, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.04,0:29:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.04,0:29:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.04,0:29:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they're karmically destined
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.30,0:29:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is a karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.80,0:29:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as karmic destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.45,0:29:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a gifted group myself
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.19,0:29:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the chances
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.51,0:29:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,we figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.59,0:29:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was in power versus force
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.25,0:29:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the chances of becoming serious
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.61,0:29:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,actually interested in enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.05,0:29:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,seriously oriented towards enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.29,0:29:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,are less than 1 in 10 million persons
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.61,0:29:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million people
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.28,0:29:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you can say
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.32,0:29:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the foremost
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.75,0:29:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,your ultimate ambition in life
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.25,0:29:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,1 in 10 million
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.31,0:29:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,will tell you to reach enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.48,0:29:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so to even be here
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.01,0:29:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you see how unusual that is
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.88,0:29:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,all the 1 in 10 millions
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.53,0:29:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,are here right now
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.31,0:30:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,each one here represents
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.75,0:30:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million people out there
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.47,0:30:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see if that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.95,0:30:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask this
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.41,0:30:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,in the name of the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.64,0:30:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,what was just
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.46,0:30:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,stated as a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.55,0:30:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,my god yes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.09,0:30:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,each one of us represents
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.98,0:30:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,10 million
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.81,0:30:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore a group like this
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.73,0:30:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,influences the collective consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.54,0:30:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.56,0:30:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a group such as this
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.24,0:30:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,influences the collective consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.00,0:30:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.09,0:30:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,not as a consequence of what we do
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.14,0:30:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,say or believe
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.01,0:30:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but by virtue of our intention
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.07,0:30:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which we have become
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.40,0:30:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill the potential
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.92,0:30:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,which Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.27,0:30:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.94,0:30:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.27,0:30:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all the great teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.38,0:30:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,taught us over time
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.46,0:30:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,we say yes to it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.70,0:30:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and we join in fulfilling that potential
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.79,0:30:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that fulfills the vision of the Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.85,0:31:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Buddha for all of us
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.33,0:31:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.68,0:31:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so we become the fulfillment of
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.51,0:31:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't say the intention of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.65,0:31:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we can say of the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.32,0:31:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,intrinsic potential
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.51,0:31:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,intrinsic to this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.38,0:31:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to the source of our own creation
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.98,0:31:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that which you affirm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.86,0:31:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes more powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,within yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.38,0:31:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if you affirm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.05,0:31:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,each and any of us
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.24,0:31:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,every one of us here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.01,0:31:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is karmically destined for enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.35,0:31:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,each and every one of us here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.92,0:31:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is destined for enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.90,0:31:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise you wouldn't be here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.66,0:31:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.29,0:31:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise you wouldn't be here
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.88,0:31:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a course in tennis
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.64,0:31:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.64,0:31:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who would be at a tennis class
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.64,0:31:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,except future tennis players
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.21,0:31:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a course on how to reach
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.71,0:31:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.71,0:32:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in the straightest
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.71,0:32:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,narrowest way that I know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.71,0:32:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore the karmic destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.35,0:32:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,has brought us all together
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.55,0:32:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why I say
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.20,0:32:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone here is a gift to me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.20,0:32:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're a great gift to me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.77,0:32:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a great gift to me
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.74,0:32:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocence and trustingness
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.46,0:32:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of your love shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.03,0:32:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.42,0:32:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.51,0:32:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's with reverence
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.66,0:32:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm aware of it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.25,0:32:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with such trust
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.25,0:32:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,goes great responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.70,0:32:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and the innocent are given to you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.00,0:32:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the responsibility is heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.50,0:32:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.86,0:33:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for your trust and love
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.55,0:33:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.27,0:33:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the fallen guru savages the trust
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.24,0:33:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocent trust
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.28,0:33:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I put my life in your hands
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.25,0:33:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,my god what more could you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.94,0:33:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.85,0:33:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see the severity
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.61,0:33:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consequence of violating it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.53,0:33:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the responsibility and you see the severity of the consequence of violating it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.82,0:33:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why a guru doesn't drop from 700 to 698
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.82,0:33:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,he usually drops from 700 to 135
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.82,0:33:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because to violate the trust at that level
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.20,0:33:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very heavy-duty energy to screw it up
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.16,0:33:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to want to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.31,0:33:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,this morning you mentioned the third eye of the Buddhic body
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.81,0:33:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,what is that Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.31,0:33:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,well I shouldn't use that terminology
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.31,0:33:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it's sort of a colic
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.31,0:34:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of esoteric rather esoteric
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.31,0:34:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,not a colic but esoteric
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.31,0:34:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes out of the buddha body it comes out of the buddha body it comes out of the buddha body it comes out of the buddha body it comes out of the buddha body it comes out of the buddha body
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.83,0:34:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes out of the buddha body it comes out of the buddha body
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.33,0:34:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes out of the bailey material
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the white brotherhood material
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.46,0:34:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's describing various phenomena within the etheric body
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.09,0:34:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the etheric body occupies the same physicality
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.09,0:34:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and within the etheric body there is the chakra system
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.36,0:34:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which most people are familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.36,0:34:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the base chakra the spleen the solar plexus the heart the heart the throat
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.26,0:34:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there are beyond the crown chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.53,0:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there are beyond the crown chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.82,0:34:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,more spiritual bodies of even higher dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.28,0:34:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,going up to lower mental, higher mental
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.13,0:34:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't recall the terminology at the moment
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.82,0:34:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's in the book though
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.15,0:34:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,yes I do in one sentence list all the various bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.86,0:34:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,from the crown chakra up
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.11,0:34:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the bodies on the way up
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.11,0:35:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the Christ body, the etymic body
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.09,0:35:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the top is the etymic body
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.57,0:35:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,below that is the Christ body, the Buddhic body
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher mental, the lower mental
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.51,0:35:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's one in between that I'm blanking on
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.40,0:35:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,causal body, yeah right
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.09,0:35:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so when spiritual advancement reaches a certain point
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.63,0:35:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity for discernment opens up
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.28,0:35:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to calibrate a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.44,0:35:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you can tell by looking at it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.90,0:35:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,this is not a person I want to hang out with
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.86,0:35:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like you get what the energy is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.92,0:35:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you get what the essence is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.84,0:35:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you get what the essence is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.86,0:35:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of it is just sort of intuitively
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.05,0:35:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so the nearest thing to it in a spiritually aligned person
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.51,0:35:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is to trust your intuition
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.96,0:35:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or at least use your intuition
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.59,0:35:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as a likelihood of God's trying to speak to you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.26,0:35:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,through some modality that is non-linear
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.07,0:35:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,some people are very adept at that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.63,0:35:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan is very adept at that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.57,0:36:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean she knows the non-linear just through a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.44,0:36:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,a knowingness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.80,0:36:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know I get a bad feeling about you taking that highway
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.15,0:36:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sure enough
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.57,0:36:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on the evening news
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.57,0:36:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a three car crack up on it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.40,0:36:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you know she like knows it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.59,0:36:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not through linear processing left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.69,0:36:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,not through intellectual
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.88,0:36:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,so because you're aligned with integrity and divine love
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.26,0:36:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher regions tend to respond to you you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher regions tend to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.26,0:36:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I say dear God I ask for your will in this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.28,0:36:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I wait for an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.92,0:36:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I say I ask for your will in this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.17,0:36:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I stop thinking about it
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.17,0:36:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then I go out in the garden and I turn on a light
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.17,0:36:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and suddenly as I'm turning the light on bang
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.34,0:36:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I got what the answer is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.65,0:36:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.42,0:36:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's not a linear process
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.38,0:36:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so prayer tends to intensify that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.25,0:37:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,asking God for God's will
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.96,0:37:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what is God's will for me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.42,0:37:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that's part of the 12 step program too
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.71,0:37:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,11th step we ask through conscious meditation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.59,0:37:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,increase our conscious contact with God
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.07,0:37:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,asking only for God's will for me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.17,0:37:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,for knowledge of his will for us
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.01,0:37:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,this couldn't be a better prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.46,0:37:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of a better one
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.11,0:37:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.57,0:37:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.53,0:37:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the original question I was going to ask
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.09,0:37:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,actually has already been answered several times
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.19,0:37:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,while I was standing in line
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.53,0:37:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,must have been a good question
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.51,0:37:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,well it was about
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.84,0:37:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a relative of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.61,0:37:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a close relative has recently been diagnosed with schizophrenia
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.38,0:37:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was going to ask how best
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.23,0:37:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what sort of attitude or orientation to adopt
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.00,0:37:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to best help this person
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.26,0:38:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess to help me accept it and manage the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.61,0:38:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as to help this person
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.57,0:38:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,grow and develop to their potential spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.73,0:38:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah you do the best you can
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.40,0:38:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,physical, mental and spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.65,0:38:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what I got
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.82,0:38:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,get the best doctor you can
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.61,0:38:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,put them on the best medication you can
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.44,0:38:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,put them on every psychological
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.80,0:38:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,assist health group therapy individual
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.38,0:38:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and then pray on top of it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.73,0:38:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and does
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.23,0:38:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and illnesses like that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.71,0:38:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes have a somewhat bizarre karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.19,0:38:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,antecedent
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.80,0:38:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't know exactly what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.92,0:38:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to pray for
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.92,0:38:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.50,0:38:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah that's what
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.44,0:38:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that was a confusing point as well
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.40,0:38:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,if you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.01,0:38:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you know wish the best for somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.88,0:38:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,do you really know what that means
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.13,0:38:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah then you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.90,0:38:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,then you take the first step
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.86,0:38:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.51,0:38:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Al-Anon program for instance
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.61,0:38:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you know you surrender them to God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.63,0:38:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and you pray for them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.28,0:38:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,send them love
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.09,0:38:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrender them to God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.26,0:38:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and you pray for them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.40,0:38:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and you pray for them
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.42,0:38:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and you surrender them to God
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.00,0:38:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and give them the best doctor you can
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.17,0:38:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the best treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.09,0:38:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,what about
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.94,0:38:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.17,0:39:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual insight versus intellectual insight
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.67,0:39:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in terms of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.71,0:39:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual development
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of somebody that doesn't have that intellectual insight
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.98,0:39:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,are they still
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.23,0:39:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you know like
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.01,0:39:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,when
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.42,0:39:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with schizophrenia
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.69,0:39:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't sometimes have that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.51,0:39:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to answer
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.03,0:39:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.11,0:39:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so can you still
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.46,0:39:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,have a spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.84,0:39:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yeah sure
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.01,0:39:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,insight
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.53,0:39:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,even though the intellect is gone
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.36,0:39:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.86,0:39:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.25,0:39:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.63,0:39:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.76,0:39:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.26,0:39:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and I experienced many miraculous things
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.13,0:39:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in treating schizophrenic patients
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.51,0:39:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.76,0:39:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I you know brought in
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.59,0:39:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and wrapped up in wet sheets
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.32,0:39:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.76,0:39:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and squirming on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.50,0:39:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,totally demented
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.44,0:39:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said within myself
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.05,0:39:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I held his mudra
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.94,0:39:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I got
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.51,0:39:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the spirit within
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.55,0:39:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.71,0:39:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you could see the peace within
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,another time
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.38,0:39:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,patient's laying on the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.63,0:39:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,catatonic
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.63,0:40:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the nurse is in the nursing office
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.63,0:40:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm holding in mind for him
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.63,0:40:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I could see
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.88,0:40:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I could intuit what was going on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.88,0:40:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you're blaming God
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.88,0:40:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,for what is the consequence of the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.88,0:40:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden he jumped off the floor
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.88,0:40:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and began talking
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.92,0:40:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the nurse crossed herself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.92,0:40:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.92,0:40:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.92,0:40:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so all those things are at one time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.92,0:40:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what you can do for them
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.21,0:40:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
