Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.48,0:57:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,astral projecting all over the place having wild adventures erotic adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.40,0:57:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,he gets back into his body and there's his wife next to him in the bed and he's
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.51,0:57:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,had all these erotic adventures out there so he's struck by guilt besides in
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.59,0:57:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,those days nobody heard anything about such things so he was a pioneer all
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.84,0:57:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.96,0:57:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,, so Monroe was wandering around the astral dimensions you see and there
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.71,0:58:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't any information about it so and then he would come back in the body he's
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.32,0:58:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,an engineer so he'd make careful notes of you know scientific notes of what
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.61,0:58:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,phenomena very interesting you saw your heart started goes out to him because of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.78,0:58:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,his naivete yeah he also gets involved with some rather negative energies you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.78,0:58:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,know climb on his back and try to claws claw him out to death etc then Monroe
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.51,0:58:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,found that by creating a dissonance between the two hemispheres you know
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.00,0:58:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,sonic dissonance you could potentiate an altered state of consciousness and you
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.92,0:58:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,had different levels level 12 level 10 etc that plus self-hypnosis and using
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.30,0:58:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the the art stimulation so you lay on a mat for 10 days and you do the practice
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.53,0:58:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,all this you learn how to do it at will now what's what do you learn from it
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.48,0:58:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mainly intellectual curiosity I would say primarily intellectual curiosity
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.69,0:59:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,if other dimensions in the physical seems unreal to you once you go out of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.21,0:59:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,body that you'll drop that one there are other dimensions a plenty and and as I
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.19,0:59:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,said in previous lectures that Monroe had the most incredible voice but Rose
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.26,0:59:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,voice had a profound intrinsic piece to it was that I've never heard a voice
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.78,0:59:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,like that Monroe just had a because you've worked with them yourself I did a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.51,0:59:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.86,0:59:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Monroe Monroe he just had this incredible voice of stillness and peace
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.11,0:59:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,great and is it any use not really excepting to realize that there are
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.07,0:59:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,other dimensions I've gone out of body several times spontaneously as a result
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.30,0:59:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of illness so it wasn't exactly a new to me but the fact that you could do it at
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.71,0:59:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,will then some people go out of body quite easily there's a sort of karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.71,0:59:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,inheritance or
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.92,1:00:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,she's going to body and I think back here you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.61,1:00:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just a bit of my not my way back
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.61,1:00:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,no you're trained you're trying to get a claim to come back and they wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.78,1:00:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't let you out on your own until
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.38,1:00:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,like a double whistle on that was so you come back in the body and as i've said
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.13,1:00:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that previous lectures i remember coming back in the body upside down
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.61,1:00:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah this will came and I forget where I was up
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.23,1:00:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We had made an agreement to meet somewhere out there in the semi-astral domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.23,1:00:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden we heard the whistle.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.23,1:00:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So I come back in the body and I'm looking out the back of my skull at the floor.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.23,1:00:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to back out of the body, go 180 and go back in again.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.23,1:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're scientifically trained such as I was, it's very interesting, of course, to the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.65,1:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing this work for 30 years, all kinds of discoveries.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.65,1:00:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The T.A. Gestalt and Fritz Perls and Erickson and all these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.65,1:01:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never done Monroe stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.65,1:01:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Monroe's fun and it was enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.90,1:01:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't bring you closer to enlightenment, but it will satisfy your curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.71,1:01:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.01,1:01:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,One more doubt hits the dust.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.01,1:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.01,1:01:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.82,1:01:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've talked about astral projection.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.82,1:01:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.94,1:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.94,1:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of consciousness remains the same before and after going out of body.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.40,1:01:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas the calibrated level is a major difference before and after the near-death experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.40,1:01:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Near-death experience is a major jump in consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.13,1:01:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Astral projection, the reason it doesn't make a jump in your consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.13,1:01:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and we tested that, I think, with Yaron last lecture,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.13,1:01:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is because you knew it all the time that you're spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.13,1:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You spend most of your time out there as a spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.13,1:01:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and very short amount of time as a body.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.13,1:02:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was no surprise to you when you find yourself back into that which you've been for eons.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.13,1:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.00,1:02:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.05,1:02:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Your book, I, Reality and Subjectivity, calibrates at a very lucid 999.8.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.05,1:02:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you also published that there are six people on Earth currently that calibrate above 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.09,1:02:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one above 900 would have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.09,1:02:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There were, at the time we did it, I forget, I used to have it on the blackboard.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.09,1:02:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget how many were over.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.19,1:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There was three between 600 and 700,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.40,1:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,one between 700 and 800,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.40,1:02:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,one between 800 and 900,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.40,1:02:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,one between 900 and 1,000 at the time I wrote the book, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.40,1:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Would it seem reasonable that the one that is over 900 is in Sedona at this time?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.65,1:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.65,1:02:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.65,1:02:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.96,1:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.88,1:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you've spoken many times about males having war to be able to transcend up to the 200 level.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.05,1:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.05,1:03:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Males having to go to war in order to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.05,1:03:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, to transcend.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.05,1:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,200.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.05,1:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to, but it is a very common way.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.17,1:03:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In which many a man, you bite the bullet, man, you conquer fear right then and there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.17,1:03:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, for God, for country, for the queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.17,1:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you walk right into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.17,1:03:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bam.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.07,1:03:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You never have to cross that line again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.07,1:03:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Women do in childbirth more often, I think.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.84,1:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditionally, at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.13,1:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Believing that we're going to have war with terrorism, with the Al-Qaeda,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.36,1:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with the more radical elements of Islam for possibly generations,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.36,1:04:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and that we have hundreds of thousands of young men and young women who are in the military,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.61,1:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and who are defending us in Afghanistan and Iraq right now,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.61,1:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and wherever the battlefield will be in generations.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.61,1:04:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the karmic implications for the soldier of killing?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.67,1:04:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything subserves a karmic purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.34,1:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention is what it's about.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.48,1:04:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.86,1:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a level at which you surrender the personal will for a greater good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.23,1:04:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.23,1:04:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,War is hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.63,1:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to really be pretty sophisticated to understand war.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.63,1:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, it's a karmic unfoldment of mankind in general.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.94,1:04:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, as we've mentioned, 93% of human history there's been war.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.94,1:05:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,93% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.94,1:05:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, peace is an abnormal condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.94,1:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's too apathetic to fight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.28,1:05:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Malnutrition reigns instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.28,1:05:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,7% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.28,1:05:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as though that's the only way certain things can be expressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.73,1:05:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the emergence of the ego, as you saw on the first slide,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.86,1:05:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is out of the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.86,1:05:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the animal kingdom, through the left brain in the human then,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.44,1:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,arises contention.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.48,1:05:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have enough aggression to get what you need to survive,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.59,1:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't live long enough to become a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.59,1:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to have been pretty successful.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.59,1:05:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And have been pretty successful for a couple million years to even survive.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.17,1:05:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, first comes survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.17,1:05:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then comes transcending survival of the physicalness of the animal, the left brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.28,1:06:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And at level 200, transcending into a new dominion of the province of spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.65,1:06:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, war is almost inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.65,1:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,War is almost inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.94,1:06:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever seen any, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.94,1:06:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,animals not fighting each other?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.28,1:06:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because territory is territory.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.28,1:06:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Territory is territory.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.09,1:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whole continents are warring tribes, warring tribes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.09,1:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still warring.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.53,1:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The other side of the world, they're still warring.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.53,1:06:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they're stuck back where we were not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.53,1:06:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still warring.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.59,1:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's going to have dominion over the turf?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.59,1:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all turf wars, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.59,1:06:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Turf wars.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.11,1:06:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Turf wars.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.11,1:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The left side of the brain sees turf.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.19,1:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And it fights over turf.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.78,1:07:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when you say intent is a major part of the karmic potential for the soldier killing,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.19,1:07:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have acquaintances who are soldiers, are police officers, who have killed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.30,1:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Some have no hatred for the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.30,1:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Others have intense hatred for the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.30,1:07:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.30,1:07:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So each one is different then, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.30,1:07:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.30,1:07:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.30,1:07:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In World War II, we didn't hate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.30,1:07:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The kamikazes came over, and you get strafed.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.78,1:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, or you get blown up by a mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.78,1:07:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a minesweeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.07,1:07:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So sudden death was there all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.07,1:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sudden death, sudden death was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.07,1:07:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And you learned to live with sudden death, learned to live with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.17,1:07:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you go up in pieces, you go up in pieces, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.17,1:07:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.90,1:07:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a soldier who has an intent, who has no hatred,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.00,1:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but gets the bloodlust up in the middle of battle.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.00,1:07:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're going to be working through different archetypes within yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.84,1:07:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Different chakras and different archetypes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.84,1:08:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There comes the time when you reach the level of valor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.57,1:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly the police and the firemen in 9-11 in New York City showed us what valor looks like.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.75,1:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Climbing a ladder in jeopardy of your own death and many, many hundreds of them dying, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.93,1:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They did so and sacrificed their personal self to integrity, duty, and your fellow man, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.89,1:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They fulfilled a very great karmic propensity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.68,1:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.19,1:08:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditionally, the warriors, you know, dance around and get themselves into an agitated hate-the-enemy state.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.89,1:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But a very successful warrior doesn't need that at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.11,1:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.11,1:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your duty is to sink that submarine, and that's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.31,1:09:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't hate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.31,1:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel sorry for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.72,1:09:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.85,1:09:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lousy way to go on a submarine.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.85,1:09:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.85,1:09:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to drop depth charges, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.85,1:09:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.64,1:09:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What a way to go, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.26,1:09:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Bailey spoke on glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.26,1:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the title, the complete title?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.26,1:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Briefly, what is it about?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.26,1:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she asking?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.26,1:09:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Bailey's book, Glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.26,1:09:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.26,1:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never read it, I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.26,1:09:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.26,1:09:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to read it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.26,1:09:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the title.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.26,1:09:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that is the title?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.26,1:09:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.26,1:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.26,1:09:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.26,1:09:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.26,1:09:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.26,1:09:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that you project a specialness.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.44,1:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You desire a thing, not because it's desirable, but because you project a desirability on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.44,1:10:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it has like a magical allure and an aura.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.71,1:10:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.14,1:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Television specializes in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.14,1:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Madison Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.56,1:10:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Specializes in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.78,1:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That specialness, the allure, the glamour.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.78,1:10:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Glamour is like, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.78,1:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.78,1:10:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.78,1:10:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.10,1:10:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The specialness.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.10,1:10:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Course in Miracles addresses that specialness, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.15,1:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay well.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.15,1:10:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.15,1:10:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We project specialness onto others and crave it because of the specialness that we put
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.15,1:10:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,onto it in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.15,1:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.15,1:10:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to make it, and I don't want to hear any more about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.69,1:10:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.69,1:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.69,1:10:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.69,1:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.69,1:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.69,1:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.69,1:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.69,1:10:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.69,1:10:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.52,1:10:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
