Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.52,1:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.52,1:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.22,1:10:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.22,1:10:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.22,1:10:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.23,1:10:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.27,1:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.27,1:10:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.78,1:10:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice being here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.78,1:10:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.78,1:10:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering after you've serving to God, is it okay You surrendered to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.78,1:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,was it okay in Christ Jesus being me?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.17,1:10:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,may the mind that was in Christ Jesus be in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.72,1:11:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's okay to say what, in Jesus Christ what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.31,1:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,May the mind that was in Christ Jesus be in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.52,1:11:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.52,1:11:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.75,1:11:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.94,1:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would the writing be?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.71,1:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.98,1:11:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that be a thousand?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.32,1:11:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking Christ Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.52,1:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he wants to know what that would calibrate as.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.68,1:11:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, asking Christ Jesus to be your Savior or to come into you?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.10,1:11:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.89,1:11:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's about the top of the scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.36,1:11:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's much more you can ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.44,1:11:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I am that I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.93,1:11:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That statement, would that be about the same?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.93,1:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he say, I am that I am?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.89,1:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am that I am?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.35,1:11:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you say you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.06,1:11:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am what I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.89,1:11:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you asked who...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.31,1:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, it depends on what you mean by that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.88,1:11:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in the Bible, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.60,1:11:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I think asking Christ...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.72,1:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization that...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.92,1:12:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Christ is the perfect manifestation, the fulfillment of being.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.84,1:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the source of his own creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.93,1:12:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be higher.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.05,1:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.63,1:12:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.47,1:12:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.75,1:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,As it says in the Bhagavad Gita,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.88,1:12:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that Krishna says,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.56,1:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,all who consider me as divinity are dear to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.84,1:12:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,by whatever name they call me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.52,1:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The 91st Psalm says the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.44,1:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who put their life in my hands are mine.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.39,1:13:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.06,1:13:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious to know what...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.72,1:13:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.67,1:13:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any other animals on the planet
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.64,1:13:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that have access to salvation?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.47,1:13:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know of any.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.72,1:13:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated all the levels of all the animal kingdom, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.61,1:13:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see that they eventually arrive at 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.07,1:13:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, 200 is the beginning of spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.18,1:13:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So my personal way of seeing it
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.77,1:13:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is that they are evolving to the level of humanness eventually.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.15,1:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so they may not be able to reach salvation in this lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.06,1:14:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but they could be reborn and reach salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.06,1:14:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.06,1:14:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.06,1:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's conjecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.72,1:14:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.84,1:14:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd have to research it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.84,1:14:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have to take a little time to research it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.84,1:14:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.84,1:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go directly from being a cow to the celestial realm?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.35,1:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I sort of doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.35,1:14:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.46,1:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From 200 up, you would say.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.46,1:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the animal is in an evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.56,1:14:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal is in an evolutionary sequence
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.06,1:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that eventually is going to end up as humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.60,1:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.60,1:14:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.60,1:14:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The chart that you get that's given in Truth vs. Falsehood with the animals,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.60,1:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the current consciousness level of the group calibration of animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.80,1:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The group of the species, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.80,1:14:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But like a human being can reach the level of 1000.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.80,1:15:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Could animals, their bodies, could they reach higher levels?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.63,1:15:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, could they hold the consciousness level?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.63,1:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.63,1:15:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.21,1:15:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The species, we do the species.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.21,1:15:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And the species is characteristic of that level.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.21,1:15:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when your consciousness moves higher, you evolve into a higher species, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.21,1:15:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the purpose.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.39,1:15:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I quoted from the Rig Veda, that you evolve from below on up,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.71,1:15:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become your potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.71,1:15:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your potential, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.86,1:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.63,1:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember being an animal?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.63,1:15:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.85,1:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.17,1:15:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you keep at it, you'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.17,1:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.17,1:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had permission to mention my memory was this.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.88,1:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I had permission to mention that memory was this.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.88,1:15:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't believe it anyway, so.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.88,1:15:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.88,1:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.88,1:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I think that we evolve through the entire cycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.88,1:15:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.88,1:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that we evolve through the entire cycle.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.64,1:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.64,1:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.64,1:15:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.82,1:15:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.82,1:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.85,1:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.21,1:16:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.21,1:16:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.21,1:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.92,1:16:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.92,1:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.92,1:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.92,1:16:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.30,1:16:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.30,1:16:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.30,1:16:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.39,1:16:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.39,1:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.39,1:16:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.39,1:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.39,1:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can find that in your spectrum.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.39,1:16:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.39,1:16:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because our source is divinity, and divinity is all that it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.39,1:16:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not exclusionary so why couldn't I just be a tiger at one time and a buffalo at another
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.43,1:16:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,time?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.43,1:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I emerge in humanness at the lowest level of a captured slave?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.52,1:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.52,1:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to transcend that of a captured slave and become eventually a captain of a ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.84,1:16:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.92,1:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.93,1:16:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,see evolution is simple isn't it? Well you're making it complicated. You're trying to make it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.30,1:16:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,specific instead of seeing it as a... Yeah. Gracias.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.61,1:17:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering, do you believe in synchronicity events? Synchronicity seems to be a verifiable
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.69,1:17:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,reality, yeah. So it is a truthful statement that it does exist? Yeah. Carl Jung first wrote about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.68,1:17:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Have you heard of bio-residence or bio-feedback? Well, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.52,1:17:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, speak into the mic because no one can hear you. Yeah, let me make sure I'm getting it right
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.76,1:17:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm getting senile. I don't feedback, I know about it. Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.19,1:17:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bio-residence.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.38,1:18:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you, have you heard of the concept of bio-residence? No. It's a machine that creates
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.14,1:18:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,cycles that's... No. No, you have not. There's a lot of those machines out there. Right, right, but you're
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.27,1:18:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,unfamiliar with bio-residence. Okay, do you believe in attacking the condition of bipolar
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.11,1:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that vitamins therapy might be... Attacking the position? No, I don't
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.96,1:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,believe in attacking any position. No, no, no attacking the condition... The condition.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.57,1:18:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,... of bipolar illness? Yes, it's a condition, yes. What is that? Do you believe vitamin therapy is a viable
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.57,1:18:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,process by which you can reduce the condition of bipolar? I didn't work with
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.19,1:18:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,it in the realm of bipolar, I worked it in the realm of schizophrenia. Okay, so
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.81,1:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the, in your mind there is a difference. Well, bipolar,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.96,1:18:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's a different chemistry. Yes, bipolar is a different chemistry than schizophrenia, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.96,1:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so you couldn't really take a position on treating bipolar in terms of vitamin therapy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.96,1:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.96,1:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Linus Pauling might have a position? He's dead, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.96,1:19:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he would have a position, his position would be different than yours?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.96,1:19:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. We didn't look at bipolar.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.96,1:19:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, well thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.84,1:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bipolar, you know, schizophrenia, bipolar response to like, you know, like lithium or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.96,1:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi doctor.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.96,1:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.96,1:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a conflict between remaining in the world versus surrendering the world to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.25,1:19:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not a conflict.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.47,1:19:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, sometimes is it more effective to remain in the world and then just radiate spiritual energy out?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.47,1:19:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any say over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.89,1:19:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.72,1:20:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say if I surrender, sometimes my mind will ask, if I surrender, then will I disappear and become non-available to other people?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.72,1:20:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about other people, let God worry about other people.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.72,1:20:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender the world to God, including your own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.22,1:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is the...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.98,1:20:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You get permissions to leave, and you'll either leave or not leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.31,1:20:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave, it's fantastic, and if you don't leave, it's fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.31,1:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.75,1:20:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your karmic destiny may...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.75,1:20:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.22,1:20:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care whether you are to stay or not to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.22,1:20:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.22,1:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your karmic destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.22,1:20:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you're here to enlighten other people or whether you go, if that's your karmic destiny, you're not going to have any say over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.22,1:20:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With complete surrender, you don't know what's going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.22,1:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You may walk on, you may not.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.73,1:20:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So the error is the mind presumes that it knows the way to help other people?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.73,1:20:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.73,1:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the block to be surrendered?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.73,1:21:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind doesn't know which is better, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.27,1:21:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it serves people best to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.63,1:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's on your karmic destiny as to which path you follow.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.63,1:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to heaven, they say, I see you did the world a favor, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.63,1:21:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your karma, as a person, will take over, and you will know when it's right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.63,1:21:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love the world, leave it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.63,1:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.63,1:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.15,1:21:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.72,1:21:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand in my individual sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.72,1:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And then would like the right white brotherhood be not legitimate to kind of postpone their own evolution and then remain...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.72,1:21:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not up to us to say what's legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.72,1:21:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One has freedom of choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.72,1:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.72,1:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You got something better to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.72,1:21:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.47,1:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.56,1:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.98,1:22:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.68,1:22:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I met you, my life keeps getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.68,1:22:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.68,1:22:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good sign.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.68,1:22:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.68,1:22:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Speeding up karma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.68,1:22:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.68,1:22:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.68,1:22:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Since my last update, I had emergency surgery, I almost died, lost a good friend, and I lost
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.81,1:22:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.81,1:22:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.81,1:22:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than that, things are good.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.81,1:22:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're moving along.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.81,1:22:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to get as much as I can out of, I want to learn something from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.81,1:22:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is specifically my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.81,1:22:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not that kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.81,1:22:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.81,1:22:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.81,1:22:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.81,1:22:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I was accused of sabotage and conspiracy in this company that I was in.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.64,1:23:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that whatever you affirm in yourself evokes its opposite.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.06,1:23:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So like I affirmed lovingness in myself about a year ago, and that's when everything fell
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.38,1:23:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,apart.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.72,1:23:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm wondering, do I ever see anything purely, or is everything I see a projection
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.96,1:23:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,of myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.19,1:23:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say-
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.19,1:23:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything you see is a projection.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.39,1:23:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.39,1:23:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.38,1:23:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So if someone is accusing me of conspiracy and sabotage, is that something that's actually
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.56,1:23:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in me that's being-
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.56,1:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.56,1:23:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you yourself could have done in the past, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.57,1:23:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I would pray for forgiveness for the one in me who's falsely accused others.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.46,1:23:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, now you're talking about one of the commandments.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.94,1:23:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To bear false witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.44,1:23:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very unlikely that any of us got this far in evolution without having borne false
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.86,1:23:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,witness in the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.86,1:23:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No question.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.86,1:23:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Very unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.28,1:23:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.28,1:24:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, I would say, oh Lord, I pray for forgiveness for the one in me who may
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.94,1:24:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,have borne false witness against others, and I ask for their forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.77,1:24:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, brother, for I was only seeking self-gain.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.96,1:24:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, do you presume that that was yourself in the past?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.81,1:24:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And pray for forgiveness as though you were currently guilty of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.55,1:24:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As I say, if everybody, you know, is cheating you, I say, you know, pray for the one in
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.60,1:24:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you who's cheated others in the past, because this is karma coming back, you know, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.19,1:24:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not necessarily a current condition, but it's a reflection of something.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.19,1:24:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're obviously, because of your spiritual intention, pulling up all this negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.47,1:24:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.73,1:24:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exhilarating it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.02,1:24:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And just keep forgiving it as it arises, and give thanks to the Lord that you have forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.89,1:24:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have a chance to undo all this negative karma, because nothing happens by chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.14,1:24:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore, it's coming up for reasons.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.31,1:25:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get involved in spiritual work, you can exhilarate the stack coming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.78,1:25:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have done this know about the stacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.18,1:25:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes they're, you know, a big stack, big stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.93,1:25:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Loss, gain, false witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.93,1:25:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason the commandments are commandments is because they are the most common ailments
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.05,1:25:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.05,1:25:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.05,1:25:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The lie, the stupid, the very false witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.59,1:25:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.68,1:25:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to do that in politics all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.67,1:25:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up there and absolutely lie right through their teeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.82,1:25:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie right through their teeth.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.82,1:25:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, God Almighty, the moxie, where do they get the moxie to do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.82,1:25:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.14,1:25:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the video from yesterday shows you saying what you just denied saying, you know
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.06,1:25:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.52,1:25:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So that takes some balls, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.63,1:25:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mexican word for that is more acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.28,1:25:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.28,1:25:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they call a Mexican?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.28,1:25:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.28,1:25:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it called?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.28,1:25:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cajones.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.28,1:25:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cajones.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.28,1:25:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cajones.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.28,1:25:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.28,1:25:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Cajones.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.28,1:25:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.28,1:25:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're uncorking a lot of karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.48,1:26:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go through it with grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.05,1:26:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.05,1:26:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray for grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.05,1:26:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.05,1:26:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgiveness, grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.43,1:26:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.77,1:26:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.77,1:26:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.06,1:26:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're undoing a whole stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.06,1:26:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Undoing a whole stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.65,1:26:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it comes up in big stacks like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.65,1:26:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a thousand questions, but neither one answer is going to help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.36,1:26:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.36,1:26:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.65,1:26:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.65,1:26:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.65,1:26:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.65,1:26:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.65,1:26:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.65,1:26:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.42,1:26:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.42,1:26:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask a favor?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.93,1:26:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask a favor instead?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:35.93,1:26:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rhetorical question, or are you asking a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.35,1:26:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.35,1:26:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.35,1:26:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.35,1:26:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask a favor?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.35,1:26:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.35,1:26:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have spent a lot of time and money trying to grow, and I feel stuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.81,1:26:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind go like a thousand miles a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.64,1:26:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.64,1:26:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.64,1:26:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I get a little jump by osmosis?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.64,1:26:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you get what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.64,1:26:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.64,1:26:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.64,1:27:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.64,1:27:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.59,1:27:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.59,1:27:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She gets it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.59,1:27:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she get a jump by osmosis?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.59,1:27:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.59,1:27:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You hang out with spiritual groups where peace, equanimity, easy does it, live and let live
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.56,1:27:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,are the rule, and you absorb the energy, but you get it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.50,1:27:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are groups that say, bring the body, you get it by osmosis.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.68,1:27:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you know it, you have identified with the field, and your own consciousness is now
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.61,1:27:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,dominated by the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.02,1:27:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a spiritual group that calibrates over 500 and hang out with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.02,1:27:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.02,1:27:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In the right place, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.02,1:27:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.02,1:27:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You hang out with a field that's over 500, and their way of being, their attitude, see,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.14,1:27:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because who we are expresses itself in multiple ways, not just verbiage, see, words.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.14,1:27:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Words are cheap.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.68,1:27:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How you are with everything that exists with your eye lingers over beauty or does not linger
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.53,1:28:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,over beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.53,1:28:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.53,1:28:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In a thousand subtle ways, you're demonstrating that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.53,1:28:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll go through a point where the beauty of a thing absolutely paralyzes you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.39,1:28:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't look at it because you can't function.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.98,1:28:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, you learn to live with the beauty because you see the essence, the incredible
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.98,1:28:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,perfection of all things shine forth, and you see that all is divinity in its expression,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.98,1:28:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,however it is expressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.98,1:28:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you hang out with groups that hold to high spiritual values.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.03,1:28:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold to high spiritual standards.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.03,1:28:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people in their spiritual pathway visit everybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.03,1:28:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They go to this church.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.03,1:28:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They go to that church.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.03,1:28:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They go to a bar mitzvah.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.03,1:28:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They go to whatever spiritual group.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.03,1:28:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a time in my life when I went to a different spiritual group every night.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.32,1:28:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All different ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.32,1:29:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,New age, old age, Mexican, Christian, it didn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.32,1:29:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I even said I put on a yarmulke.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.32,1:29:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the white thing and I did the Passover service.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.15,1:29:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's a period of investigation and the feeling out what's common to all of spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.15,1:29:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,integrity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.15,1:29:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a commonality no matter what they call themselves, Jewish or Christian or Islamic
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.15,1:29:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.15,1:29:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a commonality.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.73,1:29:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you turn over the beetle or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.73,1:29:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moving to Sedona to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.73,1:29:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.73,1:29:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess I am the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.73,1:29:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Already found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.73,1:29:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.73,1:29:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for a place of high spiritual intention, this is a place of high spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.73,1:29:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.73,1:29:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.73,1:29:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.73,1:29:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Sedona Tyren Auto.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.73,1:29:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona Tyren Auto.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.73,1:29:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They do the Buddhist meditations there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.73,1:29:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.73,1:29:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about as spiritual as you can get I guess.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.73,1:29:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.73,1:29:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you both for your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.73,1:29:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.73,1:29:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.73,1:29:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.73,1:29:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.73,1:29:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.73,1:29:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:58.73,1:29:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.73,1:30:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.73,1:30:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.73,1:30:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.31,1:30:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.31,1:30:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.31,1:30:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.43,1:30:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.43,1:30:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.43,1:30:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.43,1:30:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.43,1:30:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.18,1:30:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.18,1:30:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving on to another point.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.18,1:30:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.18,1:30:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Last question.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.18,1:30:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've talked about the experiential awareness of the unfolding of the divinity as the void
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.18,1:30:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is transcended.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.52,1:30:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that differ in any sense from the experiential awareness of divinity at, for example, the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.51,1:30:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,six hundreds or seven hundreds before we would transcend the void?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.28,1:30:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, each one is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.28,1:30:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then that book Transcend the Levels as I G Nazar Golden.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.28,1:30:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I go into each level.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.59,1:30:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book that's forthcoming after this one, called Devotional Non-duality, I treat
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.68,1:30:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,them rather extensively, how to transcend the void and how to avoid the trap of the
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.77,1:30:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,void.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.10,1:30:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So your subjective experiential awareness of divinity at 860 is different to the awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.03,1:30:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity at 600?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.64,1:30:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.76,1:30:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:00.07,1:31:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.46,1:31:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,860 ain't better than 600, it's just different.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.92,1:31:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.61,1:31:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a hippopotamus ain't better than an elephant, it's just different.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.05,1:31:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.71,1:31:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.82,1:31:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.85,1:31:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hippopotamus and elephant are both just profound.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.71,1:31:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're different.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.61,1:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.07,1:31:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.96,1:31:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.52,1:31:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.39,1:31:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.85,1:31:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.11,1:31:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One more?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.89,1:31:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come on, hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.88,1:31:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hustle-y bustle-y, hustle-y bustle-y.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.22,1:31:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only go to a quarter hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.81,1:31:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.18,1:31:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.82,1:31:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking me there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.86,1:31:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me you were not going to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.52,1:31:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is about karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.64,1:31:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.02,1:31:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that there is karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.35,1:31:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know if there's karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.00,1:31:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.39,1:32:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.85,1:32:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.35,1:32:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.23,1:32:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.89,1:32:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To become a human being, you got born.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.46,1:32:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am really asking a question about this one thing to have an idea about karma and to see
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.19,1:32:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it in a mental way and how it all fits, but how do you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.14,1:32:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know until you become more advanced in your consciousness and then it becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.38,1:32:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,stunningly apparent.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.38,1:32:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.38,1:32:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stunningly.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.38,1:32:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And is there something in developing consciousness that does that for you?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.22,1:32:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness increases and then it becomes obvious that there isn't such thing as an
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.39,1:32:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,isolated slice of all of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.64,1:32:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no isolated slice of all of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.09,1:32:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is a slice of a continuity, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.19,1:33:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this exist all by itself, no past, no future?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.46,1:33:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.56,1:33:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So it becomes obvious, stunningly obvious, that everything is evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.56,1:33:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the wrinkles?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.72,1:33:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.72,1:33:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That I was just born?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.72,1:33:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been here a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.22,1:33:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.22,1:33:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So evolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.52,1:33:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.52,1:33:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.52,1:33:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to say a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.52,1:33:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.86,1:33:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.48,1:33:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Even within one human existence, you see the evolution of the child becoming the girl,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.89,1:33:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming the adolescent, and then eventually the old lady.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.77,1:33:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So right now, for me, it's just a matter of faith that that will occur to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.22,1:33:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't have to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.19,1:33:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.19,1:33:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessary to believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.56,1:33:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live it as though it's true, you'll come out way ahead rather than living it
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.77,1:33:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.01,1:33:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.10,1:33:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everyone is accountable.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.67,1:34:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the field of consciousness is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.59,1:34:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything that's ever happened anywhere in time or time or space is recorded forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.31,1:34:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Recorded forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.18,1:34:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The questions that you're asking me now have already gotten recorded in consciousness forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.17,1:34:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000 years from now, we could ask, did such and such a thing occur on this stage in this
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.64,1:34:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,place?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.64,1:34:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll get an answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.64,1:34:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's recorded now forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.17,1:34:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.68,1:34:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're accumulating a record forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.93,1:34:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If that don't do for karma, I don't know what will.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.55,1:34:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.55,1:34:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for letting me come.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:43.55,1:34:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.64,1:34:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.64,1:34:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.64,1:34:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.64,1:34:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.64,1:35:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.85,1:35:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.97,1:35:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.10,1:35:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For their support.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.10,1:35:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.10,1:35:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.10,1:35:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.10,1:35:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.35,1:35:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.35,1:35:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.72,1:35:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.73,1:35:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:16.73,1:35:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just like to thank everyone for your support.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.73,1:35:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you may not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.73,1:35:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you may not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.73,1:35:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you have made some very generous donations to us and have made it possible
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.30,1:35:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to offer classes free to the public.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.30,1:35:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we want to thank you from the bottom of our heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.30,1:35:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is something the doctor and I have been trying to accomplish for about three years
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.30,1:35:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,now to where we can give free classes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.30,1:35:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And due to your generosity, it has been possible.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.30,1:35:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want to thank all of you for supporting the work.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.30,1:35:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.30,1:35:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.30,1:35:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.30,1:35:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.30,1:35:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.30,1:35:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.30,1:35:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.30,1:35:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.30,1:35:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.30,1:35:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.30,1:35:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.30,1:35:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.30,1:35:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.30,1:35:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.30,1:35:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.73,1:35:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.81,1:36:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,As a living prayer, which collectively has become a living prayer, it is influencing
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.35,1:36:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,all of mankind at the fact.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.47,1:36:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.90,1:36:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It is saying to me, what can I do to be that which you can karmically fulfill?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.09,1:36:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.09,1:36:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that way, you're profoundly influencing.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.46,1:36:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do for people in the flood?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.89,1:36:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Be the most loving human being you can be right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.43,1:36:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already raising the level for everyone, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.64,1:36:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Compassion then arises out of our compassion.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:46.10,1:36:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So we radiate forth into the world a powerful energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.22,1:36:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A collective such as this has a very powerful effect on the world and worldly events.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.97,1:37:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So we pray for the things that we think will bring about peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.93,1:37:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself am saying a prayer of thankfulness.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.39,1:37:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For the king of Saudi Arabia, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.77,1:37:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Abdullah, yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.40,1:37:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Who now is the centerpiece for the entire Islamic world to try and resolve the source of all the violence in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.77,1:37:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's certainly, I pray for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.30,1:37:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fulfillment of his desire to fulfill the potential of Islam.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.69,1:37:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which essentially is a religion of peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.86,1:37:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Religion of peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.93,1:37:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, like we said, whatever is integrous seems to pull up its opposite to try to seize control of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.85,1:37:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity went through that phase as long as it's currently going through that phase.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.73,1:37:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is pristine, just like the pieta, tends to bring forth, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.18,1:38:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if we hold in mind, if we hold in mind, what we hold in mind tends to manifest.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.31,1:38:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We hold in mind the peaceful coexistence.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.22,1:38:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Peaceful coexistence.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.59,1:38:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And by holding it in mind, then it manifests as the king of Saudi Arabia using his linear domain to bring it about as an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.56,1:38:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all together then we have a profound effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.86,1:38:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So I give thanks and I conclude as I began.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.06,1:38:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory and exultius, Dio.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.06,1:38:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Glory to God in the highest.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.89,1:38:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I give thanks, O Lord, for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.21,1:38:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my prayer coming true.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.36,1:38:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.48,1:38:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For which I give thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.56,1:38:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.77,1:39:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, look at that thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.21,1:39:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, isn't that fun?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.47,1:39:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
